name: Verso 64
author: MmcCrafter
description:
A
 Remake of my Verso 56 Palette which was for my take on a 
fantasy console color palette, The OG palette was inspired by 
the Pico 8 palette so please check it out if you don't 
know what Pico 8 is! I remade it because I felt the colors were too dull
 and there were too many whites that barely had a difference between 
them.
